Anti-Scratch and Anti-Fog options are standard on many of their glasses and special treatments are available to extend the life of your eyewear while helping you see better by filtering light and reducing glare.

When a rapid temperature change occurs, micro-water droplets in the air will easily collect on the untreated lenses impeding vision. FogLess® 3Sixty™ Technology provides the ultimate fog prevention when:Transitioning between warm and cool environmentsWorking in humid and wet environmentsEngaging in perspiring activityUsing eye protection with respiratory equipmentFogLess® 3Sixty™ was tested at length using the test method as outlined in the European EN 166/168 standard. During this test lenses are pre-treated and repeatedly exposed to moisture for an extensive period of time and wiped continuously to simulate harsh field conditions.
